{
  "texts": [
    "The reason behind the collaboration between 1D convolution and RNN is that individually each of these does not cater to the extraction of spectral-spatial features in an efficient manner.",
    "Other works mentioning collaboration between convolution operation and RNN is proposed by Hao et al. (2020).",
    "The authors extracted features using U-Net and then fed the input to LSTM to explore contextual information within features.",
    "A peculiar collaboration between techniques has been shown by Zhou et al. (2017) by employing PCA to extract spatial information.",
    "The first principle component (PC 1) lends itself in a sequential form in terms of several lines to the LSTM network."
  ]
}